OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA warm
OL,6,Fday on Friday and a little more humid
OL,7,Fwith lighter winds. Turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy through the
OL,9,Fweekend with an increasing risk of
OL,10,Fheavy showers, possibly thundery.
